permitted with the notice reproduced, use is restricted to Nordic
Semiconductor integrated circuits, and reverse engineering is prohibited. The
authoritative text is the file itself, obtainable with the SoftDevice from
https://www.nordicsemi.com/Products/Development-software/S140/Download
